<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 40px;">
    <div style="max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        
        <h2 style="color: #111827; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">Confirm your account</h2>
        
        <p style="color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px;">
            Hi {{name}},<br><br>
            Welcome to the PrepUp CBT community! To finish setting up your profile, please use the following verification code:
        </p>
        
        <div style="background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <h1 style="font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: #4f46e5; letter-spacing: 8px; margin: 0;">{{otp}}</h1>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">
            This security code expires in 10 minutes. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>

        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6; margin: 32px 0;">

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0;">PrepUp CBT • Global Education Community</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #d1d5db; margin-top: 4px;">© 2026 PrepUp. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
